## Cohesion Audit: jim-carrey.md

### Central Thesis
Jim Carrey is a Type 7 whose engine is escape from pain rather than the pursuit of joy, and his late-period "I don't exist" turn is not a breakdown but the first time a man who spent fifty years running finally stopped.

